OL,3,CTeachers thought they were 'going to
OL,4,Cdie' during Ammanford school stabbing
OL,6,FA 14-year-old pupil accused of
OL,7,Fattempted murder during a school
OL,8,Fstabbing asked a teacher, "do you want
OL,9,Fto see what's in my pocket?" before
OL,10,Fattacking her with a knife, a court
OL,11,Fwas told.
OL,13,FSwansea Crown Court heard statements
OL,14,Ffrom two teachers recorded the day
OL,15,Fafter they were injured during the
OL,16,Fknife attack at Ysgol Dyffryn Aman,
OL,17,Falso known as Amman Valley School, in
OL,18,FApril this year.
