OL,3,CTeachers thought they were 'going to
OL,4,Cdie' during Ammanford school stabbing
OL,6,FMs Elias said: "I remember thinking to
OL,7,Fmyself this could be it, I thought I
OL,8,Fwas going to die."
OL,10,FThe court was told Ms Elias had
OL,11,Fdiscovered a small kitchen knife in
OL,12,Fthe pupil's school bag during a bag
OL,13,Fcheck at the start of the school term
OL,14,Fin September 2023.
OL,16,FMs Elias said police were called
OL,17,Fduring that incident and the pupil was
OL,18,Fsuspended from the school.
